Title: A Cataloger's Paradise
Description:
<Doc Nanners looks out of breath as he hands you a letter inviting you back to the Dragonscale Expedition Basecamp for training. He eagerly tries to explain.>

Kind elf. Proud tiny-man. Many cameras. Yes?

<Doc Nanners nods excitedly, awaiting your response.>
ObjectivesText: Speak with Cataloger Coralie in the Dragonscale Basecamp.
RewardText: There are incredible new specimens to catalog everywhere you look!
